---
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 pt-20 pb-24 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-32">
  <!-- faint red glow, hero only -->
  <div
    class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_0%,_rgba(185,28,60,0.13)_0%,_transparent_70%)]"
  >
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
    <!-- trust badge -->
    <div
      class="mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-border bg-bg-card px-4 py-1.5 text-sm text-text-muted"
    >
      <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
        <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-accent opacity-75"></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
      </span>
      Non-custodial — you keep custody, always
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-balance text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-7xl">
      Earn more on your TRX.<br />
      <span class="text-accent">Keep your keys.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-balance text-lg text-text-muted sm:text-xl">
      troniti maximizes the yield on your staked TRX — claiming, restaking, voting, and
      renting out energy — through an on-chain permission that can <span class="text-text"
        >never move your funds</span
      >.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
      <a
        href="#waitlist"
        class="w-full rounded-lg bg-accent px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover sm:w-auto"
      >
        Join the waitlist
      </a>
      <a
        href="#how"
        class="w-full rounded-lg border border-border px-6 py-3 font-medium text-text-muted transition-colors hover:border-text-muted hover:text-text sm:w-auto"
      >
        See how it works
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- headline number -->
    <div class="mt-16 flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <span class="mono text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl">~15%</span>
      <div class="text-left text-sm text-text-muted">
        combined TRX yield<br />
        <span class="text-text-muted/70">voting + energy rental</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
